        <a class="rbp-card" style="--card-accent: var(--rbp-amber);" href="/pages/membership">
          <span class="rbp-card__icon">MB</span>
          <h3>Become a member</h3>
          <p>For eligible SMEs that want a structured relationship with access to selected benefits and support routes.</p>
          <span class="rbp-card__link">View membership →</span>
        </a>
        <a class="rbp-card" style="--card-accent: var(--rbp-green);" href="/pages/offers">
