          <p>For software, providers and partner-sourced offers curated around common SME needs.</p>
          <span class="rbp-card__link">Browse offers →</span>
        </a>
        <a class="rbp-card" style="--card-accent: var(--rbp-blue-2);" href="/pages/business-nbn">
